54
00:10:51.208 --> 00:10:52.499
♪ You wonder why ♪

55
00:10:52.500 --> 00:10:58.166
♪ I'm all out of tears to cry ♪

56
00:10:58.708 --> 00:11:03.541
♪ Today. I'm not afraid to die ♪

57
