76
00:14:34.375 --> 00:14:36.041
[ominous synthwave music playing]

77
00:15:04.250 --> 00:15:05.249
[gun cocks]

78
00:15:05.250 --> 00:15:06.333
[guns cocking]

79
00:15:07.416 --> 00:15:09.250
[menacing rock music playing]

80
00:15:19.708 --> 00:15:20.625
