82
00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:30.000
[energy crackling]

83
00:16:08.208 --> 00:16:09.958
[suspenseful music intensifying]

84
00:16:11.750 --> 00:16:12.790
Hold!

85
00:16:12.791 --> 00:16:13.874
[music halts]

86
00:16:13.875 --> 00:16:16.250
[refugees stammering]

87
00:16:16.833 --> 00:16:19.207
You. why do you look human?

88
00:16:19.208 --> 00:16:20.290
I am human.

89
00:16:20.291 --> 00:16:23.040
Please. we mean no harm.

90
00:16:23.041 --> 00:16:25.249
We're just trying to get to safety.

91
00:16:25.250 --> 00:16:27.082
- There's a--
- Safety?

92
00:16:27.083 --> 00:16:29.624
You're smuggling demons into our realm.

93
00:16:29.625 --> 00:16:32.124
Our only safety
is their species' extinction.

94
00:16:32.125 --> 00:16:34.082
You don't understand!

95
00:16:34.083 --> 00:16:37.416
If you'll put the guns down.
I can explain.

96
00:16:38.375 --> 00:16:39.374
[panicked clamoring]

97
00:16:39.375 --> 00:16:41.249
[predator demon snarling]

98
00:16:41.250 --> 00:16:42.708
[refugees screaming]

99
00:16:46.500 --> 00:16:47.374
[bellows]

100
00:16:47.375 --> 00:16:48.583
[epic music playing]

101
00:17:05.916 --> 00:17:08.083
DARKCOM. evacuate!

102
00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:35.000
[epic music ends]

103
00:18:06.208 --> 00:18:08.125
[sobbing]

104
00:18:17.166 --> 00:18:18.166
[delirious laughter]

105
00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:29.333
[tense. uneasy music playing]

106
00:18:57.083 --> 00:19:02.666
Now. we all
go down the rabbit hole together.

107
00:19:08.333 --> 00:19:09.332
["Devils Never Cry" plays]

108
00:19:09.333 --> 00:19:10.790
♪ Bless me ♪

109
00:19:10.791 --> 00:19:16.874
♪ With the leaf off of the tree ♪

110
00:19:16.875 --> 00:19:20.790
♪ On it. I see ♪

111
00:19:20.791 --> 00:19:24.749
♪ The freedom reign ♪

112
00:19:24.750 --> 00:19:28.624
♪ We are falling ♪

113
00:19:28.625 --> 00:19:32.457
♪ The light is calling ♪

114
00:19:32.458 --> 00:19:36.374
♪ Tears inside me ♪

115
00:19:36.375 --> 00:19:40.332
♪ Calm me down ♪

116
00:19:40.333 --> 00:19:44.124
♪ Midnight calling ♪

117
00:19:44.125 --> 00:19:48.040
♪ Mist of resolving ♪

118
00:19:48.041 --> 00:19:50.082
♪ Crown me ♪

119
00:19:50.083 --> 00:19:55.915
♪ With the pure. green leaf ♪

120
00:19:55.916 --> 00:19:59.790
♪ Praise to my father ♪

121
00:19:59.791 --> 00:20:03.707
♪ Blessed by the water ♪

122
00:20:03.708 --> 00:20:06.332
♪ Black light. dark sky ♪

123
00:20:06.333 --> 00:20:07.915
IN MEMORY OF KEVIN CONROY
(1955-2022)

124
00:20:07.916 --> 00:20:12.458
♪ The devil's cry ♪
